Rebecca Michael, a 100 level Philosophy student of the Kogi State University Ayingba, Kogi State, on Wednesday, allegedly committed suicide shortly after her boyfriend broke up with her.  According to reports, the deceased allegedly consumed a poisonous substance at her hostel in Lokoja, after a prominent DJ, Caleb Abalaka aka DJ Aka, told her that he was no longer interested in the relationship. .  Rebecca was rushed to the Federal Medical Centre after she was discovered by friends, but she later gave up the ghost and has since been buried at Lokongoma cemetery.